dct_title_s: Englewood Township in Teaneck, Bergen County, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: Map of the property of Englewood Heights Estates, Inc. with numbered lots was prepared by Joseph W. Stagg, Civil Engineer, Englewood, N.J. An official seal and signatures show approval of the plan by the Englewood town council and Teaneck township committee.
